title: Kate Winslet says 'no' to Photoshop in her L'Oreal contract
text:
Published By: USATODAY.com: Entertainment - Today 
Kate Winslet has given a big ol' veto to retouching her Lancome ads, according to her L'Oreal contract. Wear those wrinkles proudly, Kate!
